filters-protection:
A label in the filters. Other items in the same menu are:
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-type}}
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-status}}
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-project}}
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-language}}
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-wiki}}

The possible values are user groups: "autoconfirmed", "sysop", "templateeditor", etc.

filters-status-diverged:
An item that describes the status of a module or a template. Other items in the same menu:
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-status-outdated}}
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-status-ok}}
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-status-unlocalized}}
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-status-diverged}}

filters-status-ok:
'''This is not an OK button!'''

An item that describes the status of a module or a template, meaning that it's up to date and doesn't need changes.

Other items in the same menu:
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-status-outdated}}
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-status-ok}}
* {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-filters-status-unlocalized}}
